hadiths[46]{hadithnumber,text}:
248,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab ghusl farmatey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) pahley apne donon hath dhotey phir isi tarah wuzu kartey jaisa Namaz ke liye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wuzu kya kartey they. phir pani main apni ungliyan dakhil farmatey aur unse baalon ki jodon ka khilaal kartey. phir apne hathon se teen chullu sar par daltey phir tamam badan par pani baha letey.
249,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz ke wuzu ki tarah aik martaba wuzu kya, albatta paon nahi dhoey. phir apni sharmgah ko dhoya aur jahan kahin bhi gandagi lag gaee thi, usko dhoya. phir apne uper pani baha liya. phir pehli jagah se hat kar apne donon paon ko dhoya. aap ka ghusle-janabat isi tarah hua karta tha."
250,main aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik hi bartan mein ghusl kya kartey they us bartan ko farq kaha jata tha. (note : farq ke andar 6 . 298 Kg hota hai.)
251,"main ( abu-Salma (aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke bhai Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein gaey. unke bhai ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghusl ke barey mein sawal kya. to aap ne saa jaisa aik bartan mangwaya . phir ghusl kya aur apne uper pani bahaayaa. us waqt hamarey darmyan aur unke darmyan parda haail tha. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( kehtey hain ke Yazeed-bin-Haaroon, Behaz aur jaddii ne Shoba se qadr saa ke alfaz riwayat kiye hain. (note : saa ke andar 2 . 488 Kg hota hai.)"
252,wo aur unke walid ( janab Zainul-Aabedeen ( Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas they aur kuchh aur log bhi baithey huey they. un logon ne aap se ghusl ke barey mein puchha to aap ne farmaya ke aik saa kafi hai. is par aik shakhs bola ye mujhey to kafi na hoga. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke ye unke liye kafi hota tha jinke baal tum se zyada they aur jo tum se behtar they (yani Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) phir Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne sirf aik kapda pahan kar hamein Namaz padhai. (note : saa ke andar 2 . 488 Kg hota hai.)
253,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Memuna (Raziallahu anha) aik bartan mein ghusl kar letey they. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( farmatey hain ke ibne-Uena akheer umr mein us hadis ko yun riwayat kartey they Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Memuna (Raziallahu anha) se aur sahi wahi riwayat hai jo abu-Nueim ne ki hai.
254,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya main to apne sar par teen martaba pani bahata hon aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne donon hathon se ishara kya.
255,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne sar par teen martaba pani bahaatey they.
256,mere paas tumharey chacha ke betey (unki murad Hasan-bin- Muhammad ibn-Hanfiya se thi) aaey. unhon-ne puchha ke janabat ke ghusl ka kya tariqa hai? maine kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) teen chullu pani letey aur unko apne sar par bahaatey they. phir apne tamam badan par pani bahaatey they. Hasan ne is par kaha ke main to bahut baalon wala aadmi hun. maine jawab diya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baal tum se zyada they.
257,Ummul-Momenin Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye ghusl ka pani rakha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath 2 martaba ya teen martaba dhoey. phir pani apne baain hath mein lekar apni sharmgah ko dhoya. phir zameen par hath ragda. iske baad kulli ki aur naak mein pani daala aur apne chehrey aur hathon ko dhoya. phir apne sarey badan par pani baha liya aur apni jagah se hat kar donon paon dhoey.
258,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab ghusle-janabat karna chahtey to Hilaab ki tarah aik cheez mangaatey. phir (paanii ka chullu) apne hath mein letey aur sar ke daahiney hissey se ghusl ki shuruaat kartey. phir baaein hissey ka ghusl kartey. phir apne donon hathon ko sar ke beech mein lagaatey they.
259,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye ghusl ka pani rakha. to pahley Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pani ko daain hath se baain par giraayaa. is tarah apne donon hathon ko dhoya. phir apni sharmgah ko dhoya. phir apne hath ko zameen par ragad kar usey mitti se malaa aur dhoya. phir kulli ki aur naak mein pani dala. phir apne chehre ko dhoya aur apne sar par pani bahaayaa. phir aik taraf ho kar donon paon dhoey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko roomaal diya gaya. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se pani ko khushk nahi kya.
260,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghusle-janabat kya to pahley apni sharmgah ko apne hath se dhoya. phir hath ko diwar par ragad kar dhoya. phir Namaz ki tarah wuzu kya aur jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne ghusl se farigh ho gaey to donon paon dhoey.
261,main aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik bartan mein is tarah ghusl kartey they ke hamarey hath baari-baari usmein padtey they.
262,jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghusle-janabat farmatey to (pahley ( apna hath dhotey.
263,"main aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (donon mil kar) aik hi bartan mein ghusle-janabat kartey they. aur Shoba ne Abdur-Rehman bin-Qasim se, unhon-ne apne walid (Qaasim-bin-Muhammad-bin-Abii bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) se wo Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se. isi tarah riwayat kartey hain."
264,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ki koi paak bevi aik bartan mein ghusl kartey they. us hadis mein Muslim-bin-Ibraaheem (Alaihissalam) aur Wahab-bin-Jareer ki riwayat mein Shoba se ( من الجنابة‏ (ka lafz ( zyada ( hai. (yani ye janabat ka ghusl hota thaa).
265,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye ghusl ka pani rakha. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pahley pani apne hathon par gira kar unhein do ya teen baar dhoya. phir apne daahiney hath se baain par gira kar apni sharmgaahon ko dhoya. phir hath ko zameen par ragda. phir kulli ki aur naak mein pani daala phir apne chehrey aur hathon ko dhoya. phir apne sar ko teen martaba dhoya, phir apne sarey badan par pani bahaayaa, phir aap apni ghusl ki jagah se alag ho gaey. phir apne qadmon ko dhoya."
266,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye (ghusl ka (pani rakha aur parda kar diya, aap ne (pahley ghusl mein) apne hath par pani daala aur usey aik ya 2 baar dhoya. Sulaiman Aamash kehtey hain ke mujhey yad nahi rawi ( Saalim-bin abi-Jad ( ne teesri baar ka bhi zikr kya ya nahi. phir daahiney hath se baain par pani daala aur sharmgah dhoi , phir apne hath ko zameen par ya diwar par ragda . phir kulli ki aur naak mein pani daala aur chehrey aur hathon ko dhoya aur sar ko dhoya. phir sarey badan par pani bahaya . phir aik taraf sarak kar donon paon dhoey. baad mein maine aik kapda diya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath se ishara kya is tarah ke usey hataao aur aap ne us kapdey ka irada nahi farmaya."
267,"maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke samney us masla ka zikr kya. to aap ne farmaya, Allah abu-Abdur-Rehman par raham farmaai maine to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khushbu lagai phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni tamam beeviyon ( mutahraat (ke paas tashrif le gaey aur subah ko ehram us haalat mein baandha ke khushbu se badan mahak raha tha."
268,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) din aur raat ke aik hi waqt main apni tamam paak beeviyon ke paas gaey aur ye gyara (11) thin. (9 nikah ki huin aur 2 laundiyaan) rawi ne kaha, maine Anas se puchha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uski taqat rakhtey they. to Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke ham aapas mein kaha kartey they ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko tees mardon ke barabar taqat di gaee hai aur Saeed ne kaha Qatada ke waaste se ke ham kehtey they ke Anas ne unse 9 beeviyon ka zikr kya."
269,"mujhey mazi kasrat se aati thi, chunkey mere ghar main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sahibzadi (Faatima zohra (rz)) thin. isliye maine aik shakhs ( Miqdad bin-Aswad apne shagird ( se kaha ke wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske mutaalliq masla malum karein unhon-ne puchha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wuzu kar aur sharmgah ko dho (yahii kafi hai)."
270,"mein isey gawara nahi kar sakta ke main ehram baandhon aur khushbu mere jism se mahak rahi ho. to Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya, maine khud Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khushbu lagaaii. phir aap apni tamam beeviyon ke paas gaey aur uske baad ehram baandhaa."
271,maano ke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki maang mein khushbu ki chamak dekh rahi hun us haal mein ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ehram baandhey huey hain.
272,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) janabat ka ghusl kartey to pahley apne hathon ko dhotey aur Namaz ki tarah wuzu kartey. phir ghusl kartey. phir apne hathon se baalon ka khilaal kartey aur jab yaqin kar letey ke jism tar ho gaya hai. to teen martaba is par pani bahaatey , phir tamam badan ka ghusl kartey."
273,aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke main aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik bartan mein ghusl kartey they. ham donon us se chullu bhar-bhar kar pani letey they.
274,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne janabat ke ghusl ke liye pani rakha phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pahley 2 ya teen martaba apne daaein hath se baaein hath par pani dala. phir sharmgah dhoii. phir hath ko zameen par ya diwar par 2 ya teen baar ragda . phir kulli ki aur naak mein pani daala aur apne chehrey aur baazuon ko dhoya. phir sar par pani bahaya aur sarey badan ka ghusl kya. phir apni jagah se sarak kar paon dhoey. Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke main aik kapda laai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey nahi liya aur hathon hi se pani jhadney lagey.
275,"Namaz ki takbeer hui aur safein barabar ho gain, log khadey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne hujrey se hamari taraf tashrif laey. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) musalley par khadey ho chukey to yad aaya ke aap junbi (hambistari k baad ki napaki ki haalat me) (himbistari karke aaye) hain. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se farmaya ke apni jagah khadey raho aur aap wapas chaley gaey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghusl kya aur wapas hamari taraf tashrif laey to sar se pani ke qatrey tapak rahe they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz ke liye takbeer kahi aur ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz ada ki. Usman-bin-Umar se is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) ki hai Abdul-Aala ne Mamar se aur wo Zohri se. aur Auzai ne bhi Zohri se us hadis ko riwayat kya hai."
276,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye ghusl ka pani rakha aur aik kapdey se parda kar diya. pahley Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne donon hathon par pani daala aur unhein dhoya. phir apne daahiney hath se baaein hath mein pani liya aur sharmgaah dhoii. phir hath ko zameen par maara aur dhoya. phir kulli ki aur naak mein pani daala aur chehrey aur bazu dhoey. phir sar par pani bahaya aur sarey badan ka ghusl kya. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghusl ki jagah se aik taraf ho gaey. phir donon paon dhoey. iske baad maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik kapda dena chaha . to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey nahi liya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hathon se pani jhadney lagey.
277,ham beeviyon ( mutahraat ( mein se kisi ko agar janabat laahiq hoti to wo hathon mein pani lekar sar par teen martaba daaltiin. phir hath mein pani lekar sar ke daahiney hissey ka ghusl kartin aur doosrey hath se baaein hissey ka ghusl kartin.
278,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Bani-Israeel nangey ho kar is tarah nahatey they ke aik shakhs doosrey ko dekhta lekin Musa (Alaihissalam) tanha parde se ghusl farmatey. is par unhon-ne kaha ke b-khudaa Musa ko hamarey sath ghusl karne mein sirf ye cheez rukawat hai ke aap ke khasiye badhey huey hain. eik martaba Musa (Alaihissalam) ghusl karne lagey aur aap ne kapdon ko aik patthar par rakh diya. itney mein patthar kapdon ko lekar bhaagaa aur Musa (Alaihissalam) bhi iske peechhey badi tezi se daudey . aap kehtey jatey they. aey patthar ! mera kapda de. aey patthar ! mera kapda de. us arse mein Bani-Israeel ne Musa (Alaihissalam) ko nangaa dekh liya aur kehney lagey ke b-khudaa Musa ko koi bimari nahi aur Musa (Alaihissalam) ne kapda liya aur patthar ko maarney lagey. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke b-khudaa us patthar par 6 ya 7 mar ke nishan baqi hain.
279,"(eik baar ( Ayub (Alaihissalam) nangey ghusl farma rahe they ke soney ki tiddiyaan aap par girney lagiin. Ayub (Alaihissalam) unhein apne kapdey mein sametney lagey. itney mein unke rab ne unhein pukaaraa. ke aey Ayyoob! kya maine tumhen us cheez se be-niyaaz nahi kar diya, jisey tum dekh rahe ho. Ayub (Alaihissalam) ne jawab diya haan teri buzurgi ki qasam. lekin teri barkat se mere liye be-niyaazii kaise mumkin hai. aur us hadis ko Ibrahim ne Musa-bin-Aqba se, wo Safwan se, wo Ata-bin-Yasar se, wo Abu-Hurera se, wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, is tarah naql kartey hain'' jabke Ayub (Alaihissalam) nangey ho kar ghusl kar rahe they '' ( aakhir tak) ."
280,mein fateh Makka ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui to maine dekha ke aap ghusl farma rahe hain aur Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne parda kar rakha hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ye kon hain. maine kaha ke main Umme-Hani hun.
281,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) janabat ka ghusl farmaa rahe they maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka parda kya tha. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pahley apne hath dhoey , phir daahiney hath se baain taraf pani bahaya aur sharmgah dhoi aur jo kuchh usmein lag gaya tha usey dhoya phir hath ko zameen ya diwar par ragad kar) dhoya ( phir Namaz ki tarah wuzu kya. paon ke alaawa. phir pani apne sarey badan par bahaya aur us jagah se hat kar donon qadmon ko dhoya. us hadis mein abu-Awana aur Muhammad-bin-Fuzail ne bhi pardey ka zikr kya hai."
282,"Umme-Sulaim Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ki aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur kaha ke Allah Taala haq se haya nahi karta. kya aurat par bhi jabke usey ehtilam ho ghusl wajib ho jata hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, haan agar (apni mani ka (pani dekhey (to usey bhi ghusl karna hoga)."
283,"Madina ke kisi rastey par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se unki mulaqat hui. us waqt Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) janabat ki haalat mein they. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main peechhey reh kar lot gaya aur ghusl karke wapas aaya. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke aey Abu-Hurera ! kahan chaley gaey they. unhon-ne jawab diya ke main janabat ki haalat mein tha. isliye maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath baghair ghusl ke baithna bura jaanaa. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya, Subhan-Allah ! momin hargiz napak nahi ho sakta."
284,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni tamam beeviyon ke paas aik hi raat mein tashrif ley gaey. us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyon mein 9 beeviyan thin.
285,"meri mulaqat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hui. us waqt mein junbi (hambistari k baad ki napaki ki haalat me) (hambistari ke baad ki haalat me) tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mera hath pakad liya aur main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath chalney laga. aakhir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik jagah baith gaey aur main aahista se apne ghar aaya aur ghusl karke haazire-khidmat hua. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) abhi baithey huey they, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya aey Abu-Hurera ! kahan chaley gaey they, maine waqia bayan kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Subhan-Allah ! momin to napak nahi hota."
286,kaha maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha ke kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) janabat ki haalat mein ghar mein sotey they? kaha haan lekin wuzu kar letey they.
287,"umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke kya ham mein se koi janabat ki haalat mein so sakta hai? farmaya haan , wuzu karke janabat ki haalat mein bhi so saktey ho."
288,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab janabat ki haalat mein hotey aur soney ka irada kartey to sharmgah ko dho letey aur Namaz ki tarah wuzu kartey.
289,kya ham janabat ki haalat mein so saktey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya haan lekin wuzu karke.
290,umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke raat mein unhein ghusl ki zarurat ho jaya karti hai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wuzu kar liya kar aur sharmgah ko dho kar so jaa.
291,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab mard aurat ke chaar zaanu mein baith gaya aur uske sath hambistari ke liye koshish ki to ghusl wajib ho gaya, is hadis ki mutabiat (pairavi) Amr ne Shoba ke waaste se ki hai aur Musa ne kaha ke ham se Aban ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Qatada ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Hasan Basri ne bayan kya. usi hadis ki tarah . abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ye hadis us baab ki tamam hadison mein umda aur behtar hai aur ham ne dusri hadis (Usman aur ibn-Abii-Ka'b ki) sahaba ke ikhtilaf ke peshe-nazar bayan ki aur ghusl mein ehtiyat zyada hai."
292,"unhon-ne Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke mard apni biwi se ham-bistar hua lekin inzal nahi hua to wo kya karey? Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Namaz ki tarah wuzu kar ley aur zakar (sexual part) ko dho ley aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye baat suni hai. maine iske mutaalliq Ali-bin-Abii taalib, Zubair-bin-Awaam, Tal'ha-bin-Ubaidullaah, Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha to unhon-ne bhi yahi farmaya Yahya ne kaha aur abu-Salma ne mujhey bataya ke unhein Urwa-bin-Zubair ne khabar di, unhein Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke ye baat unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni thi."
293,unhon-ne puchha : ya Rasulullah ! jab mard aurat se hambistari karey aur inzal na ho to kya karey? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aurat se jo kuchh usey lag gaya usey dho ley phir wuzu karey aur Namaz padhey . abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ghusl mein zyada ehtiyat hai aur ye aakhiri hadison ham ne isliye bayan kar dein (taake malum ho jaey ke) us mas'ale mein ikhtilaf hai aur pani (se ghusl kar lena hi ( zyada paak karne wala hai. (note : ye ijazat shuruaat Islam mein thi baad mein ye hukm mansukh ho gaya) .
